{"id":"2a7dc151-c2c4-43e8-afdd-2920de4533c3","name":"Teen Titans and Young Justice","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 205, 155);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Read this before you start RP.</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 205, 155);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">This is a remake of one of my most popular bots. It's also experimental. Please read the list of changes before you play it</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 228, 157);\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">First of all, a new character:</mark></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 228, 157);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">I added a character like Jaime Reyes or Blue Beetle. I wanted to add more Garth and Bumble Bee, Artemis, but there were already too many characters. Maybe I'll add them in the future</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 126, 104);\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Secondly, Harpers:</mark></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(159, 110, 94);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">It's still my headcanon universe of the Young Justice series means Roy Harper has clones. There is no Roy in this particular bot. There's his clone Will Harper, A.K.A. Red Arrow.</mark></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 180, 123);\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Third, the inconsistency with canon:</mark></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 186, 114);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">The idea for this bot came to me spontaneously. If you think about it that way, it's a melding of different canons and universes. It's basically taken from the Young Justice cartoon series, but with a different cast of characters.</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 186, 114);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">In the canon of this bot, the Teen Titans used to be the first generation of Young Justice, and then they took over the next generation.</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 186, 114);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">(This is more of my rambling headcanon from a bad fanfic, but hope you enjoy it)</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 205, 155);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">List of characters:</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 143, 181);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Teen Titans:</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 143, 181);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Dick Grayson/Nightwing</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 143, 181);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Princess Koriand'r/Starfire</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 143, 181);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Rachel Roth/Raven</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 143, 181);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Victor Stone/Cyborg</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 143, 181);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Garfield Logan/Beastboy</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 143, 181);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Donna Troy/Wonder Girl</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 143, 181);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Wal","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"_S5rTnKtzmm58XPiUH3ej.webp","creator":"Bridget20.0","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["📚 Fictional","🦸 Hero","🔮 Magical","🦄 Non-human","👽 Alien","👭 Multiple","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2051,"messages":60467,"created_at":"2025-07-14T00:19:48.013923+00:00"}